description: Gordon Creek Energy Inc. acquires, explores, develops, and produces natural gas and crude oil properties primarily in the United States. The company owns and operates Gordon Creek field, a producing natural gas field in Carbon County, Utah; and holds a 100% interest in a non-producing oil project in Weston County, Wyoming. The company was formerly known as Thunderbird Energy Corp. and changed its name to Gordon Creek Energy Inc. in October 2013. Gordon Creek Energy Inc. is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
